<CONTENT id="_3793169_1"><TITLE value="Presentation"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;p&gt;.&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884675_1" alt="" width="125" height="101" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The following video shows the complete "plan" to protect an organisation's data&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N8xEgSe5RwE" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Data Security: Protect your critical data (or else) (youtube.com)&lt;/a&gt; (7 min)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This video gives examples of how Hash algorithms test Integrity and provide non-repudiation for digital documents&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VUI89yBDcdk" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Hashing and Digital Signatures - SY0-601 CompTIA Security+ : 2.8&lt;/a&gt; (10 min)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The following link gives a more detailed discussion on the Data Storage Network solutions&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.backblaze.com/blog/whats-the-diff-nas-vs-san/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;NAS vs. SAN - What Are the Differences Between Them (backblaze.com)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
